### Commit Convention

This project uses [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/):

- `feat:` new features
- `fix:` bug fixes
- `docs:` documentation changes
- `style:` formatting changes
- `refactor:` code refactoring
- `test:` adding tests
- `chore:` maintenance tasks

